Notes: Sometimes when adding resources to CKAN, users mistakenly add a link to the page containing links to the data rather than the data itself. This extension attempts, for a given resource to find the actual resources on the page. This will only cover some cases and isn't a solution that will fix every problem. By using an assortment of CSS, XPath and Regex on a per url (or per publisher) basis it is possible to find the important links in a HTML page
